    tmp = ((0.70 / (v1 + 0.35 - v1 + 0.67)) * (wp.abs(v0 + 0.20) * wp.cos(v1 + 0.90)))
    v1 = wp.sin(((tmp + 0.31 - tmp + 0.34) + wp.sin(v0 + 0.14)))
